column14: We are building one landscape per condition
Cancer (Apc loss and oncogenic Kras) organoid monoculture
Median CCAT score for a condition and cluster combination
Median velocity score for a condition and cluster combination
Median L1 norm distance cells from a cluster. Cells with lower distances are closer to the center of a particular cluster and viceversa.
Miminum distance of cells within a particular cluster. Cells with this value as their distance are the cluster centroid (or part of the 1% of distant outliers that have been overwritten)
Marks cells identified to be at the border/outline of a cluster as per the alphashape algorithm
Computed from the metrics above and used to build the landscape
